	<p>First of all, its not like we would get as much benefit out of a pet aug<br />
as the trinity (Bst, Necro, Mage).  <br />
<br />
10% boost to hps, dps on Doggie wouldnt be anything close to 10% of the other 3.<br />
<br />
Just like a cold nuke focus is best in wizard/dru hands but shaman/bst/ranger can use it.<br />
<br />
Would it really overpower, to put Shm on all these items.<br />
Perhaps this should be added to our 10 Class Definition Items?</p>
	
	
	
	
	
